OL,3,CTaking a look back at Blackpool
OL,4,CTower's 130-year history
OL,6,FBlackpool Tower is one of the North
OL,7,FWest's major landmarks which has
OL,8,Fattracted billions of tourists for
OL,9,Fover a century.
OL,11,FThe landmark that sits along the Fylde
OL,12,Fcoastline was built back in May 1894
OL,13,Fand visitors of the seaside resort
OL,14,Fhave been climbing up the Tower for
OL,15,F130 years.
OL,17,FThe Tower Eye gives visitors a
OL,18,Ffantastic view across the Irish Sea as
OL,19,Ffar as the Isle of Man.
