OL,3,CTaking a look back at Blackpool
OL,4,CTower's 130-year history
OL,6,FOne man who knows the iconic landmark
OL,7,Flike the back of his hand is Dave Hume
OL,8,Fwho worked there for three decades and
OL,9,Fhas done everything from changing
OL,10,Flightbulbs to painting the tower.
OL,12,FDave said: "I was chipping the
OL,13,Fpainting, knocking the loose paint
OL,14,Foff, knocking the rust off, and then
OL,15,Fpainting it to make sure that it was
OL,16,Fall good to go again."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/6
