OL,3,CTaking a look back at Blackpool
OL,4,CTower's 130-year history
OL,6,FDave said the colour of the paint used
OL,7,Ffor the tower was called "tower red"
OL,8,Fwhich he said is "not the best colour
OL,9,Fto light up unfortunately as it just
OL,10,Fabsorbs all the light".
OL,12,FHe added: "There are better colours,
OL,13,Fbut you can't change the colour
OL,14,Fwithout Government permission."
OL,16,FDave worked as a rigger for the tower
OL,17,Fwhich involves maintaining the
OL,18,Fattraction's structure, a job that
OL,19,Fneeded a head for heights and a strong
OL,20,Fstomach.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/6
