OL,3,CTaking a look back at Blackpool
OL,4,CTower's 130-year history
OL,6,F"We had nothing to hold onto, you just
OL,7,Fwalked across the steel-work to get to
OL,8,Fwhere you needed to be," he said.
OL,10,FThe tower includes other attractions
OL,11,Fsuch as the famous Tower Ballroom and
OL,12,Fthe ever popular Tower Circus which is
OL,13,Fthe oldest of its type in the world.
OL,15,FAs well as being responsible for the
OL,16,Fupkeep of Blackpool Tower, Dave also
OL,17,Fworked in the ballroom where Strictly
OL,18,FCome Dancing is filmed, helping to
OL,19,Fchange and clean the chandeliers every
OL,20,Fyear.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/6
