OL,3,CTaking a look back at Blackpool
OL,4,CTower's 130-year history
OL,6,FEvery year, 14 giant chandeliers are
OL,7,Fcarefully lowered to be individually
OL,8,Fcleaned, polished and dusted.
OL,10,FThe Blackpool Tower Circus opened its
OL,11,Fdoors in 1894 and has not missed a
OL,12,Fseason since, not even during the two
OL,13,FWorld Wars.
OL,15,FDave recalls a moment where he was
OL,16,Fwalking through the back of the circus
OL,17,Fwhere he encountered "a tiger on a
OL,18,Fload of straw bells having an
OL,19,Foperation on its tooth."
